text: Paras Sehrawat (born 3 December 1997) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Nagaland in the 2018–19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. He made his first-class debut for Nagaland in the 2018–19 Ranji Trophy on 20 November 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for Nagaland in the 2018–19 Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy on 22 February 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Nagaland cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
